ygData.messageBody:
Hi all, I am a new to this list so if this has been discussed before please
forgive me.
I am a lvl 24 woodelf warrior. Beginning to think I'm the only woodelf
warrior :) I have been kos since the beginning by the Darven City Guards.
After oh 12-15 kills I left, made my way to Freeport and other places to do
my levelling. I have swam around to get to unrest but some named npc still
found me by dags cauldron and whacked me. I now WANT to go home. I want to
go to mistmoore. Is it something I said, did, didn't do? They always say
something like I'm not a believer?? Of What? Can I raise factions? How?
Really sorry for all the questions but I want to go to my homeland and can
not, safely anyway. I'm a woodelf for crying out loud, not a dark race.
Any and all help is greatly appreciated.

Tan the homeless woodelf.
